[{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0004","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-32781","title":"Apollo Portal 配置中心未授权访问漏洞","description":"Apollo 配置中心 Portal 在 2.5.0 版本之前存在未授权访问漏洞。当目标环境启用了 configView.memberOnly.envs 配置时，低权限认证用户可直接向 /envs/{env}/releases/{releaseId} 接口发送请求，通过构造有效的 release ID 绕过权限校验，获取其未被授权的应用或命名空间的配置发布数据。该接口未调用 UserPermissionValidator.shouldHideConfigToCurrentUser 进行权限检查，导致敏感配置信息泄露。攻击者需拥有 Portal 的低权限账号并知晓目标 release ID，攻击门槛较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.5,"aliases":["CVE-2025-32781","GHSA-jxpj-9j24-w337"],"sources":["ghsa"],"published":"2026-07-12","updated":"2026-07-13","remediation":"升级 Apollo Portal 至 2.5.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复未授权访问问题。修复提交为 apolloconfig/apollo@362735d，对应 PR #5378。如无法立即升级，可启用 configView.memberOnly.envs 配置并严格限制环境访问权限，同时在网关或反向代理层对 GET /envs/{env}/releases/{releaseId} 接口添加额外的身份校验中间件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/apolloconfig/apollo/security/advisories/GHSA-jxpj-9j24-w337","https://github.com/apolloconfig/apollo/pull/5378","https://github.com/apolloconfig/apollo/commit/362735ded4f13b62f6ab9df135d7096066e8e291","https://github.com/apolloconfig/apollo/releases/tag/v2.5.0"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0001","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0001.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-45422","title":"Proximus b-box 路由器 UPnP 访问控制不当漏洞","description":"Proximus b-box 路由器 UPnP 功能存在访问控制不当漏洞（CWE-284）。已获得路由器管理权限的攻击者可利用该缺陷绕过正常的访问限制机制，未经授权直接修改端口转发规则，导致内部网络服务被意外暴露至公网，增加被远程攻击的风险。该漏洞影响 Proximus b-box v8c.725A 版本，CVSS 评分 8.1，危害等级高。建议用户及时关注厂商固件更新以修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.1,"aliases":["CVE-2025-45422"],"sources":["cnnvd"],"published":"2026-07-09T21:16:54.167","updated":"2026-07-10T18:53:55.130","remediation":"建议立即登录 Proximus b-box 路由器管理后台（通常为 192.168.1.1），在「维护」或「系统」页面检查固件更新，将固件升级至 v8c.725A 及以后修复版本。如厂商尚未发布补丁，可在「高级设置」中关闭 UPnP 服务（取消勾选「启用 UPnP」），并限制管理界面仅允许内网 IP 地址访问，以防止攻击者从外部网络利用该漏洞修改端口转发规则。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://b-box.com","http://proximus.com","https://github.com/Cedrico03/CVE-2025-45422---Bbox","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln-metrics/cvss/v3-calculator?vector=AV:L/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:C/C:H/I:H/A:H/E:H/RL:U/RC:C/CR:H/IR:H/AR:H/MAV:N/MAC:L/MPR:N/MUI:N/MS:C/MC:H/MI:H/MA:H&version=3.1"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2025/POC-AVE-2025-0001.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0001.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0002","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-58151","title":"Xapi varstored 条件竞争漏洞","description":"varstored 是 Xapi 工具栈中处理虚拟机 UEFI 变量的核心组件，其与虚拟机内部的 OVMF 通过共享缓冲区进行通信。由于缺少足够的编译器内存屏障，共享缓冲区中的数据存在 TOCTOU（时间检查与使用时间）竞态条件漏洞，攻击者可通过提前修改共享缓冲区内容来操控跳转表中的索引，可能导致任意代码执行或信息泄露。该漏洞影响使用 Xapi 工具栈的虚拟化平台，CVSS 评分 9.4，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.4,"aliases":["CVE-2025-58151"],"sources":["cnnvd"],"published":"2026-07-09T16:16:33.817","updated":"2026-07-09T17:16:56.770","remediation":"升级 varstored 到包含 CVE-2025-58151 修复的版本，具体可通过更新 Xapi toolstack 至最新补丁版（关注 XenServer/XCP-ng 厂商安全公告）。如无法立即升级，可在 VM 配置中禁用 UEFI 启动并切换为 BIOS 模式作为临时缓解措施，或限制对受影响 VM 的管理操作并发数以降低竞争窗口命中概率。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://xenbits.xen.org/xsa/advisory-478.html","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2026/01/27/2","http://xenbits.xen.org/xsa/advisory-478.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0002.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0013","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0013.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-22741","title":"RiceTheme Felan Framework 反射型跨站脚本漏洞","description":"WordPress Felan Framework 插件（由 RiceTheme 开发）1.1.3 及之前版本中存在反射型跨站脚本（XSS）漏洞。该漏洞源于程序对用户输入参数在生成 Web 页面时未进行充分的中和过滤，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制 URL，诱使用户点击后导致恶意脚本在用户浏览器中执行，造成敏感信息泄露、会话劫持等危害。CVSS 评分 7.1，危害等级高，攻击复杂度低，无需用户特权即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.1,"aliases":["CVE-2025-22741"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2026-05-27T09:16:26.977","updated":"2026-06-17T08:49:42.513","remediation":"立即联系 RiceTheme 获取修复版本，或确认是否有 1.1.3 以上更新。如无法升级，部署 Web 应用防火墙（如 Wordfence、Patchstack）拦截反射型 XSS 攻击流量；同时在 WordPress 配置中添加 `Content-Security-Policy` 响应头限制脚本来源作为临时缓解措施。也可考虑暂时禁用 Felan Framework 插件直至官方补丁发布。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://patchstack.com/database/wordpress/plugin/felan-framework/vulnerability/wordpress-felan-framework-plugin-1-1-3-reflected-cross-site-scripting-xss-vulnerability?_s_id=cve","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/2025/22xxx/CVE-2025-22741.json","https://github.com/topscoder/nuclei-wordfence-cve/blob/a47e10c73e8cfa90d75f3b72e70fb0d1cf7c5530/nuclei-templates/2025/CVE-2025-22741-felan_framework-3be71ddf-bb6f-492f-8d89-d0d850b27233.yaml","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/94ba69fdac5ced9eb8795ce09aa042cbb168d31b/2025/22xxx/CVE-2025-22741.json","https://github.com/zzzteph/low-hanging-vulns/blob/e01cbd1436b3805fae6aac0fdbaa88371dfa18db/nvd/2025/HIGH/CVE-2025-22741/README.md","https://github.com/TMA84/cvealert/blob/4e58fc35977c7899e2fc4be00dae1c243ec507c4/content/posts/cve-2025-22741.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2025-22741.md","https://github.com/adysec/hwpoc/blob/e2c3d33b7e2870449a687c9b1cfa4c48990c946b/docs/2026/WordPress_Felan_Framework_%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%84%E5%9E%8B_XSS_%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E_CVE-2025-22741.toml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/a2f3ff3fa5db5c7705ebd942909ec114df063700/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2025-22741-felan_framework-3be71ddf-bb6f-492f-8d89-d0d850b27233.yaml","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc48b6c04c59ceff2d71da45cd843fc1d449dc48/CVE/data/2025/CVE-2025-22741.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/3508ccc52a2baed6a1946843005e8957c7067f39/CVE-2025/CVE-2025-227xx/CVE-2025-22741.json","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-22741"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0013.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0088","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0088.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-37164","title":"HPE OneView 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"HPE OneView 存在远程代码执行漏洞（CWE-94），攻击者可通过特制请求利用该漏洞，在无需身份认证的情况下远程执行任意代码。该漏洞源于对用户输入的代码注入过滤不严，CVSS 评分达 10.0，危害等级严重。成功利用可导致服务器完全受控，影响 HPE OneView 系列管理平台，建议立即更新至修复版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2025-37164"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-12-16T17:16:07.843","updated":"2026-06-17T09:15:17.283","remediation":"立即将 HPE OneView 升级至 11.00 或更高版本。如无法立即升级，可在管理界面限制对 OneView 管理端口的网络访问，仅允许受信任的管理员 IP 连接，并在防火墙层面阻断非必要的 443/8443 端口外部访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://support.hpe.com/hpesc/public/docDisplay?docId=hpesbgn04985en_us&docLocale=en_US","https://github.com/rapid7/metasploit-framework/blob/master/modules/exploits/linux/http/hpe_oneview_rce.rb","https://support.hpe.com/hpesc/public/docDisplay?docId=hpesbgn04985en_us&docLocale=en_US#vulnerability-summary-1","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2025-37164","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-37164.yaml","https://github.com/g0vguy/CVE-2025-37164-PoC","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/f8a21b0c30953d5926478bb080c200645e84a23a/2025/CVE-2025-37164.json","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/010b0aa4fab18a47a1dfa699acc027ecfea23b55/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-37164.yaml","https://github.com/rapid7/metasploit-framework/blob/fcd24bcde44c83907fc2e965d2d0edd0cb92051b/modules/exploits/linux/http/hpe_oneview_rce.rb","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/0f1885b9ad0c36bab067e4e3d61739350d154cdf/data/by-cve/CVE-2025-37164.md","https://github.com/gelusus/wxvl/blob/0190a57b50c784bda47a3b9ac049eaf5bb577d6e/doc/2026-01/%E3%80%90%E5%9C%A8%E9%87%8E%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E3%80%91HPE%20OneView%20%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-2025-37164).md","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/aaa966adf56b88bf2eba7f47ee24a777c6208719/2025/CVE-2025-37164/README.md","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2025/CVE-2025-37164.rules","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/2025/37xxx/CVE-2025-37164.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/CVE-2025-37164_2.yaml","https://github.com/g0vguy/CVE-2025-37164-PoC/blob/41cc3143397bd0426f3b8971700476779ecb64ab/CVE-2025-37164.py","https://github.com/rxerium/CVE-2025-37164","https://github.com/LACHHAB-Anas/Exploit_CVE-2025-37164","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-37164"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2025/POC-AVE-2025-0088.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2025/EXP-AVE-2025-0088.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0088.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0106","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0106.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-55182","title":"React Server Components 反序列化远程代码执行漏洞","description":"React Server Components 的 RSC 协议存在反序列化漏洞（CWE-502），react-server-dom-parcel、react-server-dom-turbopack 与 react-server-dom-webpack 三个包未能安全校验 HTTP 请求中 Server Function 端点的载荷数据，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可发送特制的序列化请求触发该漏洞，导致远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 React 19.0.0 至 19.2.0 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。React 官方已发布修复版本 19.2.1 及更新。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2025-55182"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-12-03T16:15:56.463","updated":"2026-06-17T09:41:24.913","remediation":"立即将 react-server-dom-webpack/react-server-dom-parcel/react-server-dom-turbopack 升级至 19.0.1、19.1.2 或 19.2.1 及以上版本。若使用 Next.js，按对应版本线升级至 14.2.35/15.0.8/15.1.12/15.2.9/15.3.9/15.4.11/15.5.10/16.0.11/16.1.5。若使用 React Router/Waku/Vite RSC 插件，同步升级 react、react-dom 及对应 RSC 包至最新版。无法立即升级时，在反向代理/WAF 层对 /_rsc 等 Server Function 端点实施访问控制或禁用 RSC 功能作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://react.dev/blog/2025/12/03/critical-security-vulnerability-in-react-server-components","https://www.facebook.com/security/advisories/cve-2025-55182","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2025/12/03/4","https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=46136026","https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/security/china-nexus-cyber-threat-groups-rapidly-exploit-react2shell-vulnerability-cve-2025-55182/","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2025-55182","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/52506","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-55182.yaml","https://github.com/NathanJ60/react2shell-interactive","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-55182.md","https://github.com/superagent-ai/superagent/blob/5adc62db2c209b32ac0e273e9b92b62d41ce0a35/docs/README.md","https://github.com/KingOfBugbounty/KingOfBugBountyTips/blob/cd5a4a0c4b7240cbc62217cdee39cfb14be9b2dc/Readme.md","https://github.com/coreruleset/coreruleset/blob/3cfcb53d9b64f662d864c10bc7a8c2c0a99fe2ea/CHANGES.md","https://github.com/Cillian-Collins/CVE-2025-55182/blob/a0a88b790d4da73e71b09528ad4943786dd8713f/CVE-2025-55182.py","https://github.com/Mr-xn/RedTeam_BlueTeam_HW/blob/cbac586d62eedd75114b6f0aa1d8c994fef0ed87/hw%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE.md","https://github.com/Tencent/AI-Infra-Guard/blob/0015c0e437d71f8474e290d9cab3f0f8aabaca42/CHANGELOG.md","https://github.com/ejpir/CVE-2025-55182-research/blob/bd11446e5b2e5d7de83a616caddf7bdf3691b21f/src/App.js","https://github.com/ramimac/aws-customer-security-incidents/blob/fdb6cbbb8d13646746f3826f45d68c6eb2f4de33/ACTORS.md","https://github.com/Vu1nT0tal/yarb/blob/fe34c96fa0c3e342923b70996e9e4e8c13583c7f/archive/2025/2025-12-12.md","https://github.com/assetnote/react2shell-scanner","https://github.com/msanft/CVE-2025-55182","https://github.com/lachlan2k/React2Shell-CVE-2025-55182-original-poc","https://github.com/ejpir/CVE-2025-55182-research","https://github.com/mrknow001/RSC_Detector","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-55182"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2025/POC-AVE-2025-0106.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2025/EXP-AVE-2025-0106.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0106.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0040","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0040.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-8693","title":"Zyxel DX3300-T0 操作系统命令注入漏洞","description":"Zyxel DX3300-T0 固件版本 5.50(ABVY.6.3)C0 及之前版本存在操作系统命令注入漏洞，经过认证的攻击者可通过向 CGI 程序的 \"priv\" 参数注入恶意操作系统命令，在目标设备上以 root 权限执行任意命令。该漏洞允许攻击者完全控制受影响设备，危害等级高（CVSS 8.8），建议用户立即升级至修复版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.8,"aliases":["CVE-2025-8693"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-11-18T02:15:45.410","updated":"2026-06-17T10:07:27.083","remediation":"立即将 Zyxel DX3300-T0 固件升级至 5.50(ABVY.6.4)C0 或更高版本（联系 Zyxel 技术支持获取固件文件）。如无法立即升级，确保设备 WAN 访问保持默认关闭状态，并设置强密码且定期更换，防止攻击者通过认证后利用 priv 参数注入操作系统命令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.zyxel.com/global/en/support/security-advisories/zyxel-security-advisory-for-uncontrolled-resource-consumption-and-command-injection-vulnerabilities-in-certain-4g-lte-5g-nr-cpe-dsl-ethernet-cpe-fiber-onts-security-routers-and-wireless-extenders-11-18-2025","https://github.com/CV