请求，在 t_total 参数中注入 shell 元字符执行任意系统命令，导致未经身份认证的远程代码执行。该漏洞影响大量使用 CWP 面板的 CentOS 服务器，CVSS 评分 9.0，危害等级严重。厂商已在 0.9.8.1205 版本中修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.0,"aliases":["CVE-2025-48703"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-09-19T18:15:36.620","updated":"2026-06-17T09:30:12.133","remediation":"立即将 Control Web Panel (CWP) 升级至 0.9.8.1205 或更高版本。升级命令：`sh <(curl -fsSL https://control-web-panel.com/install/update.sh)`。如无法立即升级，可在 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）层面配置访问控制，限制 `/myuser/index.php` 路径仅允许可信 IP 访问，并删除或限制 `filemanager` 模块的未授权调用权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://fenrisk.com/rce-centos-webpanel","https://control-webpanel.com/changelog","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2025-48703","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-48703.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-48703.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/f8a21b0c30953d5926478bb080c200645e84a23a/2025/CVE-2025-48703.json","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/010b0aa4fab18a47a1dfa699acc027ecfea23b55/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-48703.yaml","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/a7fcebc1b9e9a88d443be844dae279be54e22ef4/data/2025/CVE-2025-48703-Sq-CC_CVE-2025-48703.md","https://github.com/wooluo/nuclei-templates-2025hw/blob/37e9617426e2a696c8c338b15df99abd6294a4eb/cve-2025-48703.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/aaa966adf56b88bf2eba7f47ee24a777c6208719/2025/CVE-2025-48703/README.md","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2025/CVE-2025-48703.rules","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/2025/48xxx/CVE-2025-48703.json","https://github.com/cloudflare/cloudflare-docs/blob/6ca38245cd4f76ea240e519a68d43bb56ac01013/src/content/changelog/waf/2025-08-04-waf-release.mdx","https://github.com/cyberdudebivash/cyberdudebivash-ai-security-hub/blob/13403e1745f63237e7ef6d51562fb36112320d77/frontend/cve/CVE-2025-48703.html","https://github.com/Skynoxk/CVE-2025-48703","https://github.com/itstarsec/CVE-2025-48703","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-48703"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0099.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0008","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0008.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-10035","title":"Fortra GoAnywhere MFT 许可证 Servlet 反序列化命令注入漏洞","description":"Fortra GoAnywhere MFT 的许可证 Servlet（License Servlet）存在不安全的反序列化漏洞。由于该组件在验证许可证响应时仅依赖可被合法伪造的签名，具备有效伪造签名的攻击者能够构造并反序列化由攻击者完全控制的任意对象，进而在服务器端触发命令注入，实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响运行 Fortra GoAnywhere MFT 的相关版本，攻击者可经网络远程利用，无需身份认证即可通过特制的许可证响应请求达成利用，CVSS 评分为 10.0，危害等级为严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2025-10035"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-09-18T22:15:41.857","updated":"2026-06-17T08:27:33.740","remediation":"立即将 GoAnywhere MFT 升级至 7.6.3 或 7.8.4 及以上版本以修复 License Servlet 反序列化漏洞。升级前请确认许可证响应签名验证机制已正确配置，升级后重启 License Servlet 服务。若暂无法升级，建议在防火墙层面限制对 License Servlet 路径的访问，仅允许可信 IP 访问，并监控异常出站连接作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.fortra.com/security/advisories/product-security/fi-2025-012","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2025-10035","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-10035.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-10035.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/c2672e36893bd220d6f65c955e260796d11ed64b/2025/CVE-2025-10035.json","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/010b0aa4fab18a47a1dfa699acc027ecfea23b55/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-10035.yaml","https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/bc433784ede7dbd633c8f5b318929cce6dea621a/rules-emerging-threats/2025/Exploits/CVE-2025-10035/proc_creation_win_exploit_cve_2025_10035.yml","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/9e669818e6334d592d44717c5ec3d75ca4cc97e4/data/2025/CVE-2025-10035-rxerium_CVE-2025-10035.md","https://github.com/vuldb/cyber_threat_intelligence/blob/6a5017307e035c2b54c7afbe3bd8582497eafa96/campaigns/c/CVE-2025-10035/README.md","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2025/CVE-2025-10035.rules","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/2025/10xxx/CVE-2025-10035.json","https://github.com/cloudflare/cloudflare-docs/blob/6ca38245cd4f76ea240e519a68d43bb56ac01013/src/content/changelog/waf/2025-09-24-emergency-waf-release.mdx","https://github.com/hack007x/veil_poc/blob/5cfe1da6e975ba816d728597885a5c5e79bda8bd/cves/2025/CVE-2025-10035.poc","https://github.com/rxerium/CVE-2025-10035","https://github.com/ThemeHackers/CVE-2025-10035","https://github.com/sentinel-aidefense/CVE-2025-10035","https://github.com/orange0Mint/CVE-2025-10035_GoAnywhere","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-10035"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0008.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0032","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0032.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-51482","title":"Letta AI代理框架 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Letta AI代理框架（letta-ai Letta 0.7.12及之前版本）的 `/v1/tools/run` 接口存在代码注入漏洞（CWE-94）。由于服务端对用户提交的 `source_code` 参数缺乏有效的沙箱隔离与输入验证，远程攻击者可通过向该接口发送特制的JSON请求，注入恶意Python代码并利用 `os.popen` 等函数执行任意系统命令，从而完全控制目标服务器。该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS评分8.8，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.8,"aliases":["CVE-2025-51482"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-07-22T17:15:33.750","updated":"2026-06-17T09:35:37.930","remediation":"升级至 Letta 最新版本（≥v0.16.8），该版本已通过 JSON 序列化替代 pickle 传输、模块白名单机制、E2B 沙箱集成等多层加固修复工具执行端点的代码注入漏洞。如无法立即升级，应立即执行以下缓解措施：（1）在反向代理（Nginx/Cloudflare）层面限制 `/v1/tools/run` 端点仅允许受信来源 IP 访问；（2）将 Letta 容器以非 root 用户运行（如 UID 1000）并启用 `--read-only` 只读文件系统；（3）在配置中启用 E2B 外部沙箱（设置 `E2B_API_KEY`）替代默认的本地目录沙箱执行工具代码，阻止任意系统命令执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/letta-ai/letta","https://github.com/letta-ai/letta/pull/2630","https://www.gecko.security/blog/cve-2025-51482","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-51482.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-51482.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/f8a21b0c30953d5926478bb080c200645e84a23a/2025/CVE-2025-51482.json","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/d09fb918849614ec417315b66ba20a16a39f16a4/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-51482.yaml","https://github.com/SourByte05/Vulnerability-Wiki-PoC/blob/e52a2c3eaf2fb0befc721cf0919d07ea435a23b4/2025/Letta-CVE-2025-51482-%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C/Letta-CVE-2025-51482-%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C.md","https://github.com/gelusus/wxvl/blob/0190a57b50c784bda47a3b9ac049eaf5bb577d6e/doc/2026-01/Letta%20%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%20(CVE-2025-51482).md","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/a7fcebc1b9e9a88d443be844dae279be54e22ef4/data/2025/CVE-2025-51482-Kai-One001_Letta-CVE-2025-51482-RCE.md","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2025/CVE-2025-51482.rules","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2025/51xxx/CVE-2025-51482.json","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/aaa966adf56b88bf2eba7f47ee24a777c6208719/2025/CVE-2025-51482/README.md","https://github.com/hack007x/veil_poc/blob/5cfe1da6e975ba816d728597885a5c5e79bda8bd/cves/2025/CVE-2025-51482.poc","https://github.com/Kai-One001/Letta-CVE-2025-51482-RCE","https://github.com/c0gnit00/CVE-2024-51482","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-51482"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2025/POC-AVE-2025-0032.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2025/EXP-AVE-2025-0032.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0032.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0100","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0100.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-53770","title":"Microsoft SharePoint Server 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft SharePoint Server 本地部署版本中的 ToolShell 组件存在反序列化漏洞（CWE-502），未经身份认证的攻击者可通过网络向目标系统发送特制的恶意请求触发该漏洞，成功利用可在目标服务器上远程执行任意代码。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 9.8，危害严重，且已有公开的利用代码在野传播。Microsoft 建议用户在官方安全更新发布前立即启用缓解措施以防止被利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-2025-53770"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-07-20T01:15:30.777","updated":"2026-06-17T09:38:51.660","remediation":"Microsoft 尚未发布针对 CVE-2025-53770 的正式安全更新，作为临时缓解措施：1）在 SharePoint 管理中心启用 AMSI（反恶意软件扫描接口）集成，并在所有 SharePoint 服务器上部署 Microsoft Defender 防病毒和 EDR 方案；2）使用 PowerShell 执行 Set-SPMachineKey 和 Update-SPMachineKey 轮换 ASP.NET 计算机密钥，然后运行 iisreset.exe 重启 IIS；3）无法启用 AMSI 时应立即将面向公网的 SharePoint 服务器断网隔离；4）审查 IIS 日志中是否存在 Referer 为 /_layouts/SignOut.aspx 且 POST 至 /_layouts/15/ToolPane.aspx 的可疑请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://msrc.microsoft.com/update-guide/vulnerability/CVE-2025-53770","https://arstechnica.com/security/2025/07/sharepoint-vulnerability-with-9-8-severity-rating-is-under-exploit-across-the-globe/","https://github.com/kaizensecurity/CVE-2025-53770","https://msrc.microsoft.com/blog/2025/07/customer-guidance-for-sharepoint-vulnerability-cve-2025-53770/","https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=44629710","https://research.eye.security/sharepoint-under-siege/","https://therecord.media/microsoft-sharepoint-zero-day-vulnerability-exploited-globally","https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/microsoft/microsoft-sharepoint-zero-day-exploited-in-rce-attacks-no-patch-available/","https://www.cisa.gov/news-events/alerts/2025/07/20/microsoft-releases-guidance-exploitation-sharepoint-vulnerability-cve-2025-53770","https://www.darkreading.com/remote-workforce/microsoft-rushes-emergency-fix-exploited-sharepoint-toolshell-flaw","https://www.forbes.com/sites/daveywinder/2025/07/20/microsoft-confirms-ongoing-mass-sharepoint-attack---no-patch-available/","https://x.com/Shadowserver/status/1946900837306868163","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2025-53770","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/52405","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-53770.yaml","https://github.com/J4ck3LSyN-Gen2/CVE-2025-53770","https://github.com/0xMarcio/cve/blob/3b956963db597dfc3808b14bb6c1e0feecc70f0a/2025/CVE-2025-53770.md","https://github.com/CrowdStrike/logscale-community-content/blob/970f85669d8ec0fe07e65f13f7120fbbc26a1bb5/Queries-Only/Helpful-CQL-Queries/CVE-2025-53770%20-%20SharePoint%20ToolShell.md","https://github.com/lal0ne/vulnerability/blob/5b9f397c1970203b1764fb7a66a0ffac39bef4cc/Microsoft/CVE-2025-53770/README.md","https://github.com/zan8in/afrog/blob/2f4b82909698139f3589d577b113dd4e51dc5c96/pocs/afrog-pocs/CVE/2025/CVE-2025-53770.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-49706.md","https://github.com/k8gege/k8gege.github.io/blob/0562c0ddc0b76d93df268fcb4feea3f97fa3589d/p/cve-2025-53770.html","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/a7fcebc1b9e9a88d443be844dae279be54e22ef4/data/2025/CVE-2025-53770-n1chr0x_ZeroPoint.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2025/CVE-2025-53770.json","https://github.com/Neo23x0/signature-base/blob/43b2b2faafdaeb7f00102673f62555a2feb04c1b/yara/expl_sharepoint_jul25.yar","https://github.com/Threekiii/CVE/blob/b15267648d6c329465c8b4cfbeb7597850ead8c1/2025/2025.07/CVE-2025-53770%EF%BC%9AMicrosoft%20SharePoint%20Server%20%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E.md","https://github.com/peiqiF4ck/WebFrameworkTools-5.5-enhance","https://github.com/soltanali0/CVE-2025-53770-Exploit","https://github.com/MuhammadWaseem29/CVE-2025-53770","https://github.com/hazcod/CVE-2025-53770","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-53770"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2025/POC-AVE-2025-0100.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0100.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0044","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0044.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-25257","title":"Fortinet FortiWeb Fabric Connector SQL注入漏洞","description":"Fortinet FortiWeb 的 Fabric Connector 组件存在 SQL 注入漏洞（CWE-89），由于对用户输入的特殊元素未能正确过滤，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标设备发送特制的 HTTP 或 HTTPS 请求触发该漏洞，导致执行未经授权的 SQL 命令，进而可能实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 FortiWeb 7.6.0 至 7.6.3、7.4.0 至 7.4.7、7.2.0 至 7.2.10 及 7.0.0 至 7.0.10 等多个版本，CVSS 评分 9.8，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-2025-25257"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-07-17T16:15:34.723","updated":"2026-06-17T09:00:34.647","remediation":"立即将 FortiWeb 升级至 7.0.11、7.2.11、7.4.8 或 7.6.4 及以上版本。如无法立即升级，可临时禁用 HTTP/HTTPS 管理接口作为缓解措施。同时建议限制仅信任 IP 访问管理界面，并启用 IPS 规则防护 SQL 注入攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://fortiguard.fortinet.com/psirt/FG-IR-25-151","https://packetstorm.news/files/id/210193/","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/52473","https://github.com/0xbigshaq/CVE-2025-25257","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2025-25257","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-25257.yaml","https://github.com/mr-r3b00t/CVE-2025-25257","https://github.com/watchtowrlabs/watchTowr-vs-FortiWeb-CVE-2025-25257","https://github.com/TheStingR/CVE-2025-25257","https://github.com/aitorfirm/CVE-2025-25257","https://github.com/imbas007/CVE-2025-25257","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-25257"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0044.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0016","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0016.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-30762","title":"Oracle WebLogic Server Core 认证机制缺失漏洞","description":"Oracle WebLogic Server Core 组件存在关键功能认证机制缺失漏洞（CWE-306），未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过 T3、IIOP 协议向目标服务器发送特制请求，绕过身份验证机制，成功利用后可未授权访问服务器中的敏感数据，甚至获取全部可访问数据的完全访问权限。该漏洞影响 WebLogic Server 12.2.1.4.0、14.1.1.0.0 及 14.1.2.0.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。Oracle 官方已发布安全补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2025-30762"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-07-15T20:15:30.567","updated":"2026-06-17T09:09:18.940","remediation":"立即从 My Oracle Support 下载并安装 Oracle 2025 年 7 月关键补丁更新 (CPUJul2025)，为 WebLogic Server 12.2.1.4.0/14.1.1.0.0/14.1.2.0.0 应用对应补丁。如无法立即更新，可在 WebLogic 管理控制台禁用 T3 和 IIOP 协议，或在网络层面限制对 7001/7002 端口的未授权访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.oracle.com/security-alerts/cpujul2025.html","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-30762"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0016.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0039","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0039.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-7523","title":"金和 OA C6 DelTemp.aspx XML外部实体注入致任意文件读取漏洞","description":"金和协同管理平台 C6 版本的 DelTemp.aspx 页面存在 XML 外部实体注入（XXE）漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 XML 请求，利用外部实体引用机制读取服务器上的任意敏感文件（如配置文件、系统文件等），导致信息泄露。该漏洞影响金和 OA C6 系列版本，CVSS 评分 5.5，危害等级中危。目前漏洞利用细节已公开，建议用户及时升级或采取访问控制措施。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.5,"aliases":["CVE-2025-7523"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-07-13T07:15:22.320","updated":"2026-06-17T10:05:08.377","remediation":"立即联系金和厂商获取 C6 安全补丁包；临时缓解措施：在应用服务器 XML 解析器中禁用外部实体解析（设置 libxml_disable_entity_loader(true) 或禁用 DTD），在 WAF 层拦截 POST 请求中包含 `<!ENTITY`、`<!DOCTYPE` 等 XXE 特征 payload 的请求，并对 `/c6/Jhsoft.Web.message/ToolBar/DelTemp.aspx` 路径实施 IP 白名单访问控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/BigMancer/Jinhe-OA-XXE-Vulnerability","https://github.com/BigMancer/Jinhe-OA-XXE-Vulnerability?tab=readme-ov-file#proof-of-concept","https://vuldb.com/?ctiid.316220","https://vuldb.com/?id.316220","https://vuldb.com/?submit.611183","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-7523.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2025/7xxx/CVE-2025-7523.json","https://github.com/SourByte05/Vulnerability-Wiki-PoC/blob/e52a2c3eaf2fb0befc721cf0919d07ea435a23b4/2025/%E9%87%91%E5%92%8CC6%20DelTemp.aspx%20XML%E5%AE%9E%E4%BD%93%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E8%87%B4%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-2025-7523)/%E9%87%91%E5%92%8CC6%20DelTemp.aspx%20XML%E5%AE%9E%E4%BD%93%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E8%87%B4%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-2025-7523).md","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/6ce62c4fb53e185987a087a07544538a62587799/2025/7xxx/CVE-2025-7523.json","https://github.com/sec-dojo-com/cve-poc/blob/0d273a0b2821f58c8dfa9e9b4a2ad049f300e8ec/pocs/2025/CVE-2025-7523.md","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/115c94bd1da3cc18977d652d6e78c9f4a5dfc13b/data/type/xxe.txt","https://github.com/Hashmire/cpeApplicabilityGeneratorPages/blob/4588dccb1f913705444975eb2a5eb79962bf2513/generated_pages/CVE-2025-7523.html","https://github.com/damn77789/nuclei-pocs/blob/81fb60243f8c8e930e9c4f1b65e2110e6e5a9204/folder-6/poc-yaml-jinher-deltemp-aspx-xxe-cve-2025-7523.yaml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2025/07/GHSA-qh6p-rhwf-c956/GHSA-qh6p-rhwf-c956.json","https://github.com/8irdy/wiki_poc/blob/9c0ae2f6d619bb358f3db31aef3970dd5a0be7f8/2025HW_Vulnerability/%E9%87%91%E5%92%8CC6_DelTemp.aspx_XML%E5%AE%9E%E4%BD%93%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E8%87%B4%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-2025-7523).md","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-7523"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0039.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0046","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0046.toml","cve_id":"无","title":"金和OA TaskReportConfirm.aspx SQL注入漏洞","description":"金和OA（协同管理平台）的 TaskReportConfirm.aspx 接口存在 SQL 注入漏洞。攻击者可在未授权的情况下向该接口传递特制的恶意参数，拼接执行任意 SQL 语句，进而窃取数据库中的敏感数据（如用户凭证、系统配置），甚至可能通过写 WebShell 等方式获取服务器控制权。该漏洞利用难度低，无需复杂权限认证，对部署了相关版本金和OA的企业内网构成严重威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["HWPOC-2025-000f81e9"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-07-10","updated":"2025-07-10","remediation":"联系金和网络官方获取安全补丁，升级至修复此漏洞的最新版本。临时措施：在 IIS 中添加 URL 重写规则，对 TaskReportConfirm.aspx 的传入参数进行严格过滤，拦截 select/union/insert 等 SQL 关键字；部署 WAF 规则防御 SQL 注入攻击。代码层面应改用参数化查询替代字符串拼接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0046.toml"}]